text: KAGR-LP (92.1 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Arapahoe, Nebraska. The station is owned by The Evangelical Lutheran Trinity Cong. of Arapahoe, NE. It airs a religious format. The station was assigned the KAGR-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on February 13, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * AGR-LP AGR-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in Nebraska Category:Furnas County, Nebraska
